OpenPerps adds an on-chain Solana program wrapper (crates/program),
client SDK, and frontend around the engine. These additions are the
part Percolator intentionally left out of scope: the entrypoint, account
validation, SPL custody, and the trading surface. Their independent review
status is tracked in SECURITY.md.
